      "content": "That makes sense. I'm seeing a lot of different angles in news reports though. Some people are saying these investigations are actually pretty essential to keep the economy healthy, while others say they're just a way for the government to mess with innovation. From what you've seen, is there a general consensus on which side has the stronger legal footing right now?",
